{"tid":27654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有線中國組：內地新措施限制資金外流】","createTime":"2016-12-07T12:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T07:55:59.000Z","uid":58309,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f45944cba18f67515695ac2511fccc59a93cea97","tid":27654,"uid":58309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:45:03.000Z","msg":"中國國民請加油換美金👍🏻😎<br />\n有生之年终於可以看到支爆😎<br />\n<br />\n【有線中國組：內地新措施限制資金外流】<br />\n <br />\n內地外匯儲備連續第五個月減少。<br />\n <br />\n有經濟學者警告，以國內每人每年換五萬美元計，只要再多兩千萬人兌換，外匯儲備很快會見底。<br />\n<br />\n亦因為這個原因，當局近期不斷推出新措施限制資金外流。<br />\n <br />\n留意稍後《有線中國組》節目，會有詳細報道。<br />\n <br />\n今晚 9:30 凌晨 00:30 有線新聞台<br />\n <br />\n‪＃有線新聞‬　有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/597474853777920/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F597474853777920%2F&d=IqCGO%2FSGJSZuJdiLoLtBvwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=e627030a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/597474853777920/</a>"},{"pid":"2370f2b619cad1bbd08f7eb42bde460e1e851556","tid":27654,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:47:32.000Z","msg":"唔比換邊個換就係資助外國勢力，等同漢奸"},{"pid":"9bce4824fc68945b0981cfc6c89d7b98c40807db","tid":27654,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:13:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5828fad0fb09bb0f4431541394b2dbd5910b49f","tid":27654,"uid":35410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:18:36.000Z","msg":"除咗資金，最好限制埋支那人外流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8014fba7095e35fb69a87679ba8dcc8cfd0d9132","tid":27654,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:50:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除咗資金，最好限制埋支那人外流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n華生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji